{"tid":1624094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修目標嘅定位","createTime":"2019-10-05T02:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:26:35.000Z","uid":54392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1404c41e24d49e3bec1f0f3361c10cf21eb00766","tid":1624094,"uid":54392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"小小個人愚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先強調絕非五毛，支持裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我覺得裝修嘅鋪頭要好小心去揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭號必須裝修：政府建築物（除咗司法機構），黨鐵站，美心，黑社會旗下嘅鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其他我覺得就真係要好小心處理，特別係中移動同銀行，唔好比其他人有機可乘去偷野，外界包括外國人只會入哂我地數，所以一定要好小心去選擇鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於藍絲鋪頭我都唔建議搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只因政見唔同就搞人，我地同佢地有咩分別呢咁，所以要分清搞嘅對像係紅定藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，支持前線所有決定，絕對唔想再有手足出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 唔岩聽就由個post 沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea1ca0aa46022459301aef2c120da5d737d5493","tid":1624094,"uid":293446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1404c41e24d49e3bec1f0f3361c10cf21eb00766","tid":1624094,"uid":54392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"小小個人愚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先強調絕非五毛，支持裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我覺得裝修嘅鋪頭要好小心去揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭號必須裝修：政府建築物（除咗司法機構），黨鐵站，美心，黑社會旗下嘅鋪頭<img src=\"/asset